General.Name: Greencity Acquisition Corp
General.Description: Greencity Acquisition Corporation does not have significant operations. The company intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses in the Internet and high technology, financial technology, logistics, clean energy, health care, consumer and retail, energy and resources, food processing, manufacturing, and education sectors in Asian market. Greencity Acquisition Corporation was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Shanghai, China.
